
'''''The Constant Gardener''''' ni filim iri ituruka muri England and German yasohotse muri 2005 iyoborwa na  Fernando Meirelles <ref>The Constant Gardener | Culture | The Guardian</ref>. Amashusho yakozwe na Jeffrey Caine ashingiye ku gitabo cya John le Carré cyo mu 2001 cyitwa The Constant Gardener <ref>What does the title “The Constant Gardener” mean? | Read <nowiki>https://the-take.com</nowiki> › read › what-does-the-title-athe-co...</ref>. Iyi nkuru ikurikira Justin Quayle ( Ralph Fiennes ), umudipolomate w’Ubwongereza muri Kenya<ref>The Constant Gardener filming locations in Kenya <nowiki>https://www.legendarytrips.com</nowiki> › trip › the-constant-ga...</ref>, ubwo yageragezaga gukemura ikibazo cy’iyicwa ry’umugore we Tessa ( Rachel Weisz ), uharanira Amnesty, asimburana n’ibintu byinshi byerekana amateka y’urukundo rwabo<ref>The Constant Gardener | Development Education Review <nowiki>https://www.developmenteducationreview.com</nowiki> › issue-5</ref>.

Iyi filime yafatiwe amashusho ahitwa Loiyangalani no mucyaro cya Kibera, igice cya [[Nairobi]], muri [[Kenya]]<ref>The Constant Gardener movie review (2005) | Roger Ebert <nowiki>https://www.rogerebert.com</nowiki> › reviews › the-constant-ga...</ref> . Ibintu muri kariya gace byagize ingaruka ku bakinnyi ndetse no ku bakozi ku buryo bashizeho Constant Gardener Trust kugira ngo batange uburezi bw'ibanze kuri iyo midugudu<ref>'Constant Gardener' lives and breathes on Fiennes's ... <nowiki>http://www.collegiatetimes.com</nowiki> › lifestyle › constant-gard...</ref>. Uyu mugambi washingiye ku buryo budasobanutse ku rubanza rwabayeho i Kano, muri Nijeriya<ref>Claim: LeCarre's "The Constant Gardener" Was Based on Pfizer Trovan Case - CBS News</ref> . Impapuro za DVD zasohotse muri Amerika ku ya 1 Mutarama 2006 no mu Bwongereza ku ya 13 Werurwe 2006<ref>The true story of how multinational drug companies took liberties with African lives | The Independent | The Independent</ref>. Ubwitonzi bwa Justin ariko bwitondewe kubihingwa bye ninsanganyamatsiko yagarukaga, aho ishusho ya firime yakomotse<ref>Constant Gardener reaps fresh crop of awards - The Guardian <nowiki>https://www.theguardian.com</nowiki> › jan › film.filmawards</ref>. Hubert Koundé, Danny Huston, Bill Nighy, Pete Postlethwaite, na Donald Sumpter bakoranye<ref>The Constant Gardener · BIFA - British Independent Film Awards <nowiki>https://www.bifa.film</nowiki> › film › the-constant-gardener</ref>. Iyi filime yagenze neza kandi yinjiza amafaranga menshi kandi yegukana ibihembo bine bya Oscar, yegukana umukinnyi wa filime witwaye neza muri Rachel Weisz<ref>INTERVIEW: RACHEL WEISZ on 'THE CONSTANT ... <nowiki>https://ianwinterton.co.uk</nowiki> › interview-rachel-weisz-on-t...</ref>.

